      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n\u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\"\r\n      alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003ePrice Optimization App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      Empowering businesses to determine optimal pricing strategies, maximizing revenue potential effortlessly.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eKey Features\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Browse for File: Click on the \"Browse\" link located under the \"Load File\" section.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Select Product Size: Choose the size of the product, for which you want to find the maximum pricing, from the dropdown menu.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Model Prediction: Click on the \"Get Prediction\" button to get the Revenue versus Price visualization graph and the Maximum price, revenue and RPI\u0027s against the product.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Business Validation: Finally the \"Run Laddering\" button will use the model prediction data to optimize the revenue based on the laddering method.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Calculates the Price Elasticity for each SKU, helping you make informed and strategic pricing decisions to optimize revenue.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
